metadata.description: After sinking the Elves' Pension Fund into some questionable altcoin investments, Santa is responding to letters via NFT to recover his losses. Santa.eth is the first interactive co-creation project from Ensemble. Collectors submit their letter to Santa via our letter writing app, accessible through the Ensemble Discord. Metadata will be batch updated with Santa.eth's responses December 23.
metadata.name: Santa.eth Letter #01
